---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Editorial Policy - TaxPortal" description="TaxPortal editorial policy and content guidelines.">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-canvas dark:bg-primary">
    <main class="min-h-screen">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-ink mb-8 dark:text-on-primary">Editorial Policy</h1>
        
        <div class="prose max-w-none space-y-6 text-body dark:text-muted">
          <p>TaxPortal is committed to providing accurate, reliable, and up-to-date tax information. Our editorial policy ensures that all content meets strict quality and accuracy standards.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4 dark:text-on-primary">Content Accuracy</h2>
          <p>All tax information is thoroughly researched and reviewed against official government sources, including tax authority publications, legislation, and official guidance. We strive to present information that is current at the time of publication.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4 dark:text-on-primary">Professional Review</h2>
          <p>Content is reviewed by qualified tax professionals and subject matter experts to ensure technical accuracy and clarity. Complex topics are simplified without sacrificing precision.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4 dark:text-on-primary">Updates and Corrections</h2>
          <p>Tax laws and rates change frequently. We regularly update our content to reflect the latest changes and promptly correct any errors identified by users or reviewers.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4 dark:text-on-primary">Disclaimer</h2>
          <p>All information provided on TaxPortal is for general informational purposes only and does not constitute professional tax advice. Users should consult qualified tax professionals for advice specific to their circumstances.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>
